pull.title: [tests] Add node methods to test framework
pull.body:
First step towards #10082:

- moves `initialize_chain()` and `initialize_chain_clean()` in their entireties to be methods of BitcoinTestFramework. At the moment, these are only ever called by BitcoinTestFramework, so it makes sense to move them to be class methods.
- add wrapper methods for start / stop nodes functions to BitcoinTestFramework class
- [trivial] restructures ordering of members of BitcoinTestFramework for clarity.

events.body: looks reasonable. Have you been able to figure out why Travis is timing out?

> Have you been able to figure out why Travis is timing out?

Because I messed up the merge :( Should be fixed now.
